    "synopsis": "After the slaughter at Isstvan V, Malcador the Sigillite quietly summons one operative from each Officio Assassinorum clade — Vindicare sniper, Eversor berserker, Venenum poisoner, Callidus shapeshifter, Culexus null and Vanus infocyte — and forges them into an Execution Force with a single brief: kill the Warmaster. While the killers cross the void towards Horus on Dagonet, a parallel manhunt unfolds on the sleepy world of Iesta Veracrux, where Arbites investigator Yosef Sabrat tracks a serial killer whose murders fit no pattern a human profiler can read. The two threads collide as a Word Bearers-engineered weapon designed to slay the Emperor himself reveals its hand.",
